<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Words Ending With -ANCE</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Scrabble Words Finder · English Solver</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The -ANCE suffix creates abstract nouns from verbs and adjectives — elegance, finance, distance. At 5 base points with the N tile worth 1 and the C worth 3, -ANCE words often reach 7-9 letters naturally, putting them in bingo territory for the 50-point bonus.</p>

<p>Learning -ANCE words also teaches you -ANT adjectives — the two suffixes share roots, doubling your vocabulary from a single pattern.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why -ANCE Matters in Scrabble</h2>

