    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5–11</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The C tile in -ANCE is worth 3 points and relatively common (2 in the bag). Most -ANCE words are 7+ letters, which means they naturally qualify for the 50-point bingo bonus — making this suffix a reliable path to high-scoring turns.</p>

